    {
      "id": "hEtV3egV7a_GM3I9sVEe2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 400.9102639306932,
      "y": -366.12908788505774,
      "width": 696.1795043945312,
      "height": 600,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "a8",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1057994456,
      "version": 1243,
      "versionNonce": 842467800,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1782408388553,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "------------\nCluster of 5 nodes\n\nNumber of nodes:\n   - e.g.: 5\n\nControl plane\n   - e.g.: 3 controllers for quorum\n\nReplication defaults\n    - default.replication.factor - fallback RF => e.g.: RF: 3    \n    - min.insync.replicas - min confirmations a write needs => e.g.: ISR: 2\n\nPartitions defaults:\n    - num.partitions\n    - Partition count is one-way. Kafka can only increase partitions.\n \nRetention\n\nTopics\n\n   - topic 1\n      - partitions: e.g. 4\n      - total replicas: e.g.: 12 (4 leaders + 8 followers)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "------------\nCluster of 5 nodes\n\nNumber of nodes:\n   - e.g.: 5\n\nControl plane\n   - e.g.: 3 controllers for quorum\n\nReplication defaults\n    - default.replication.factor - fallback RF => e.g.: RF: 3    \n    - min.insync.replicas - min confirmations a write needs => e.g.: ISR: 2\n\nPartitions defaults:\n    - num.partitions\n    - Partition count is one-way. Kafka can only increase partitions.\n \nRetention\n\nTopics\n\n   - topic 1\n      - partitions: e.g. 4\n      - total replicas: e.g.: 12 (4 leaders + 8 followers)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
